name: Decathlon Rockrider ST520 24-Speed Mountain Bike
description: Raised position., stem can be raised up to 1.18 in., ergonomic saddle: comfort that also yields greater efficiency.

name: Cannondale Scalpel HT Carbon 4 Mountain Bike
description: The Cannondale Trail SE 4 Mountain Bike is great for any rider who wants the freedom to get off the road and explore some paths and trails. Great for entry-level riders who want a little bit more than the basic, the Trail SE 4 has a Shimano Deore 10-speed drivetrain and a Suntour fork with 120mm of travel.

name: Black Diamond FirstLight Tent
description: The new Flow Manifold (patent pending) allows interior heat convection and exterior airflow to draw moisture vapor and stale air out of the tent. New, high tenacity 30D poly fabric keeps the tent tight as a drum in all conditions and is treated for flame resistance for North America compliance/availability. Available in 2 and 3 person capacity.

name: Nemo Aurora Tent
description: NEMO's award-winning Hornet Two-Person Ultralight Backpacking Tent comes in at a mere 1lb, 15oz in the two-person size, making it a light option for a pair out on a long trek or an individual looking for a little more sleeping and gear room without adding weight.

name: Sage Sonic FLy Rod
description: The Sage Sonic Rod Fly Rod is a fast-action fly rod designed for multiple applications. Built with Konnetic technology of combining carbon and resin, the rod is lighter, slimmer, and more sensitive. Lateral wobble is also minimized resulting in more accurate casting. Fly fishermen of all skill levels would use this rod.

name: Orvis Clearwater Two-Handed Fly Rod
description: Part of Clearwater's Switch & Spey series of rods, the Orvis® Clearwater® Two-Handed Fly Rod is thoughtfully designed for the value-minded angler wanting to get into two-handed casting or someone who needs a dependable backup to their favorite rod. The series ranges from lighter trout spey styles to heavier rods that are perfect for salmon and steelhead.

name: Burton Ripcord Snowboard
description: The Burton Ripcord is a great option for snowboarders on the rise who are still looking to progress their skillset. The Ripcord's tip and tail kick up with an early rise outside the feet for a catch-free confidence inducing feel. An increased pop in the tail and a more resilient nose allows for riders to easily maintain control through all terrain and conditions.

name: The North Face Men's Activist Mid Futurelight Boots
description: These boots have a waterproof and breathable membrane to ensure your feet stay dry while also not overheating. The EVA midsole gives you just the right amount of balance and cushion to make sure you're as comfortable as possible during your hike! The EXTS traction system grips on trails to give you peace of mind.

name: Golden Boy Fish Bait
description: Goldie Lock’s favorite bait - not too large, not too small - JUST RIGHT! One of the most time-tested hardbait designs, the Golden Boy is a workhorse. The bill is thin enough to have lots of great, hunting action, but strong enough that it doesn’t break or wear down after grinding it on rocks or slamming it into docks.
